"title": "8771: idolatry, objections to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8771: idolatry, objections to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture presents idolatry as absurd and irrational, offensive to God and a source of spiritual and moral danger.</p>\n<h2>Idolatry is disparaged</h2>\n<h3>The absurdity of making idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:28\">DEU 4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:18-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:18–40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:6-Isa41:7\">ISA 41:6–41:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3-Jer10:9\">JER 10:3–10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:6\">HOS 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>Idols represent falsehood and fraud</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:4\">PSA 40:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:5\">JER 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14\">JER 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17-Jer51:18\">JER 51:17–51:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:1\">HOS 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:4\">AMO 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Bowing down to idols is inappropriate</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:17-Ps135:18\">PSA 135:17–135:18</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:5-Ps115:8\">PSA 115:5–115:8</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:8\">ISA 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:15-Isa44:17\">ISA 44:15–44:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:6\">ISA 46:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:16\">JER 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:13\">MIC 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Idols contrasted with the LORD</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:5\">ISA 46:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:25-Isa40:26\">ISA 40:25–40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:24\">JER 5:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:8\">HOS 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24-Acts17:25\">ACT 17:24–17:25</a></p>\n<h2>Idolatry is forbidden by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:3-Exod20:4\">EXO 20:3–20:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:7-Deut5:8\">DEU 5:7–5:8</a></p>\n<h2>Idolatry incurs severe penalties</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:4\">ZEP 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:9\">DEU 13:1–13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:12-Deut13:15\">DEU 13:12–13:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:4\">ISA 66:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:27\">AMO 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:14\">NAM 1:14</a></p>\n<h2>God abominates idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:20\">EZK 7:20</a></strong> <em>Two terms, that is “idols” and “vile images”, meaning “abomination” are found here in parallel. A third, punning on the word for “dung” is often used by Ezekiel for idols.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25\">DEU 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:24\">2KI 23:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:9\">EZK 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:11\">EZK 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:4\">EZK 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>Pressure to worship idols must be resisted and idols abandoned</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:18\">DAN 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:20\">ISA 2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:22\">ISA 30:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:7\">ISA 31:7</a></p>\n<h2>The dangers of idolatry</h2>\n<h3>Blindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:18\">ISA 44:18</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Becoming like idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:8\">PSA 115:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:5\">JER 2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:10\">HOS 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual adultery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:16\">DEU 31:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:33\">JDG 8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:21\">ISA 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:27\">JER 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:2\">HOS 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:7\">HOS 2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:9\">HOS 8:9</a></p>\n<h3>Injustice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:7\">AMO 5:7</a></strong></p>",
